===[[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]]===
{{main|Leaf (Mythical Island 68)}}
Leaf makes an appearance as a {{TCG|Supporter}} card in [[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]]'s second expansion, {{TCGP|Mythical Island}}. Playing this card reduces the Retreat Cost of the player's Active Pokémon by 2 for the duration of the turn.

